n希望個個都可以好似天琦咁覺醒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有集光明頂話中國一味塞人嚟香港 但佢冇諗過會比人同化 因為冇數據分析 中國部門名自為政 但估唔到香港呢個大熔爐可以同化咁多中國人 <br />\n<br />\n200萬新移民係64比"},{"pid":"299c3b93a15f92908026f7c2f87cbff56c09ccf7","tid":1772840,"uid":264529,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:10:18.000Z","msg":"咪一味屌新移民<br />\n因為只要反過嚟承勢向佢地滲透民主自由<br />\n就可以化敵為友, 輸出革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86decc088c255ef8d56a424fb17d8b070f9fea70","tid":1772840,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08cf4127933a76ab3641b97089120ce125736df3","tid":1772840,"uid":173916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:22:30.000Z","msg":"天水圍都好多新移民<br />\n但好撚黃<br />\n所以唔好見人地係新移民就歧視人"},{"pid":"6fbba1ad7ea666af4bd85c35eb9be7d4c1bc7934","tid":1772840,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a63b5a6018934df6b637d6f2f483669aeee15da9","tid":1772840,"uid":155095,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T04:08:02.000Z","msg":"只係贏32票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:25:22.000Z","msg":"贏就係贏"},{"pid":"355d8e446cef3a9d165ca50837f8d7419284b352","tid":1772840,"uid":110019,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:27:48.000Z","msg":"佢贏唔係因為新移民投佢呀，係高投票率好多真香港人出嚟投佢先贏咋，on撚9，證明依家香港仲係真香港人佔多數，仲有佢只係贏32票咋，同埋七年以下果2x%仲未有資格投共狗佢先贏到咋"}]}